|en = A fictional upgrade of the destroyer main battery that was carried by the Yūgumo-class destroyers among others.
Its maximum elevation is set particularly high, but because the basic structure of its reloading system stays the same its anti-air capabilities are limited. 
However, thanks to the modifications that took various engagements into account it shall exhibit its excellent shelling power when used by Type-A as well as Type-C destroyers.

|notes = 
* Quest [[Quests#B117|B117]] reward (one of three options - requires forgoing a [[Prototype Flight Deck Catapult]]).
* Equipping this gun increases the power of Destroyer-only Night Cut-Ins by 25% for the first one, and 12.5% for the second gun. Both modifiers stack multiplicatively for a total of 40%.
** Due to the setup required for Destroyer-only cut-ins, only {{ShipLink|Tashkent}} is able to equip two guns and still perform a Destroyer-only cut-in.

|trivia = 
This gun is the modified version of the twin gun which was used by the [[:Category:Yuugumo Class|Yuugumo-class]] and the [[Shimakaze]]-class Destroyers. Which retained the depression limit of the Model C, but elevation returned to the 75° of the Model B.


